  "distanthorizons.config.client.advanced.graphics.quality.lodChunkRenderDistanceRadius": "LOD 区块渲染距离半径",
  "distanthorizons.config.client.advanced.graphics.quality.lodChunkRenderDistanceRadius.@tooltip": "遥远地平线 的渲染距离，以区块为单位。\n\n注意：这是一个尽力而为的数字。\n根据您的其他图形设置，渲染距离可能高于或低于此数字。",
  "distanthorizons.config.client.advanced.graphics.quality.horizontalQuality": "LOD 质量下降距离",
  "distanthorizons.config.client.advanced.graphics.quality.horizontalQuality.@tooltip": "质量级别之间下降的间隔距离。\n\n更高的设置将增加级别下降之间的距离，\n但会增加内存和 GPU 使用率。",
  "distanthorizons.config.client.advanced.graphics.quality.maxHorizontalResolution": "最大水平分辨率",
  "distanthorizons.config.client.advanced.graphics.quality.maxHorizontalResolution.@tooltip": "最高细节 LOD 的渲染分辨率。\n\n§6最快：§r 区块级\n§6最华丽：§r 方块级",
  "distanthorizons.config.client.advanced.graphics.quality.verticalQuality": "垂直质量",
  "distanthorizons.config.client.advanced.graphics.quality.verticalQuality.@tooltip": "LOD 表现悬垂、洞穴、悬崖面等的质量。\n\n更高的选项将增加内存和 GPU 使用率。",
  "distanthorizons.config.client.advanced.graphics.quality.horizontalScale": "水平缩放",
