  "distanthorizons.config.client.advanced.graphics.quality.blocksToIgnore.@tooltip": "定义生成 LOD 时要忽略的方块类型。",
  "distanthorizons.config.client.advanced.graphics.quality.tintWithAvoidedBlocks": "使用被忽略方块着色",
  "distanthorizons.config.client.advanced.graphics.quality.tintWithAvoidedBlocks.@tooltip": "§4注意：会使雪、地毯和活板门看起来非常糟糕§r\n被忽略的方块下方的方块是否应该获得被忽略方块的顏色？\n§6开：§r 草地上的红花会将下面的草地染成红色\n§6关：§r 跳过的方块不会改变其下方表面的颜色",
  "distanthorizons.config.client.advanced.graphics.quality.lodBias": "LOD 偏移 §6（影响原版地形）§r",
  "distanthorizons.config.client.advanced.graphics.quality.lodBias.@tooltip": "设置原版的 LOD 偏移值\n更改此值后请按 F3+T 重新加载资源包以应用。",
  "distanthorizons.config.client.advanced.graphics.quality.lodShading": "LOD 着色",
  "distanthorizons.config.client.advanced.graphics.quality.lodShading.@tooltip": "定义 LOD 应如何着色。\n可用于改善与光影的兼容性。",
  "distanthorizons.config.client.advanced.graphics.quality.grassSideRendering": "草方块侧面渲染",
  "distanthorizons.config.client.advanced.graphics.quality.grassSideRendering.@tooltip": "草方块 LOD 的侧面和底面应如何渲染？",
  "distanthorizons.config.client.advanced.graphics.quality.ditherDhFade": "淡出附近的 DH LOD",
  "distanthorizons.config.client.advanced.graphics.quality.ditherDhFade.@tooltip": "如果为开，LOD 会在您靠近时淡出。\n如果为关，LOD 会在距相机一定距离处突然消失。\n此设置受原版过度绘制预防配置的影响。",
  "distanthorizons.config.client.advanced.graphics.quality.vanillaFadeMode": "原版淡入淡出模式",
  "distanthorizons.config.client.advanced.graphics.quality.vanillaFadeMode.@tooltip": "原版 Minecraft 应如何淡入 遥远地平线 LOD？\n\n无：最快，DH 和 MC 渲染之间会有明显的边界。\n单次：在 MC 的半透明渲染之后淡入，水下的不透明方块不会淡出。\n双次：最慢，在 MC 的不透明和半透明渲染之后淡入，提供最平滑的过渡。",
  "distanthorizons.config.client.advanced.graphics.quality.dhFadeFarClipPlane": "在远裁剪平面前淡出",
  "distanthorizons.config.client.advanced.graphics.quality.dhFadeFarClipPlane.@tooltip": "DH 是否应在到达远平面之前淡出？\n这有助于防止 DH 云在远处被切断。",
  "distanthorizons.config.client.advanced.graphics.quality.brightnessMultiplier": "亮度倍率",
  "distanthorizons.config.client.advanced.graphics.quality.brightnessMultiplier.@tooltip": "LOD 颜色的亮度。\n\n0 = 黑色\n1 = 正常\n2 = 接近白色",
  "distanthorizons.config.client.advanced.graphics.quality.saturationMultiplier": "饱和度倍率",
  "distanthorizons.config.client.advanced.graphics.quality.saturationMultiplier.@tooltip": "LOD 颜色的饱和度。\n\n0 = 黑白\n1 = 正常\n2 = 鲜艳",
  "distanthorizons.config.client.advanced.graphics.quality.lodBiomeBlending": "生物群系混合",
  "distanthorizons.config.client.advanced.graphics.quality.lodBiomeBlending.@tooltip": "这是 LOD 区域的原版生物群系混合设置。\n\n请注意，除了“0”以外的任何值都会极大影响 LOD 构建时间\n并增加三角形数量。如果设置过高，对区块生成速度的成本也\n相当大。\n\n'0' 等于原版生物群系混合的 '1x1'，\n'1' 等于原版生物群系混合的 '3x3'，\n'2' 等于原版生物群系混合的 '5x5'...",

  "distanthorizons.config.client.advanced.graphics.ssao": "环境光遮蔽",

  "distanthorizons.config.client.advanced.graphics.ssao.enableSsao": "启用环境光遮蔽",
  "distanthorizons.config.client.advanced.graphics.ssao.enableSsao.@tooltip": "环境光遮蔽为方块的照明增加深度感。",
  "distanthorizons.config.client.advanced.graphics.ssao.sampleCount": "采样数量",
  "distanthorizons.config.client.advanced.graphics.ssao.sampleCount.@tooltip": "决定为遮蔽测试采样多少个空间点。\n更高的数字将提高质量并减少条带效应，但会增加 GPU 负载。",
