  "distanthorizons.config.client.advanced.debugging.lodOnlyMode.@tooltip": "如果启用，这将禁用（大部分）原版 Minecraft 渲染。\n\n注意：在此模式下启用时请勿报告任何问题！\n此设置仅供娱乐和调试。\n不保证模组兼容性。",
  "distanthorizons.config.client.advanced.debugging.renderWireframe": "渲染线框",
  "distanthorizons.config.client.advanced.debugging.renderWireframe.@tooltip": "如果启用，LOD 将渲染为线框。",
  "distanthorizons.config.client.advanced.debugging.enableDebugKeybindings": "启用调试快捷键",
